error.no_permission: Please contact the administrator to configure
open_api_notice:
You can fill in the relevant key of OpenAI/OneAPI. 
If you fill in this content, the online platform using [AI Dialogue], [Problem Classification] and [Content Extraction] will use the Key you filled in, and there will be no charge. 
Please pay attention to whether your Key has permission to access the corresponding model. 
GPT models can choose FastAI.
openai_account_setting_exception: Setting up an exception to OpenAI account
request_address_notice:
Request address, default is openai official. 
The forwarding address can be filled in, but \"v1\" is not automatically completed.
third_party_account_desc: The administrator can configure third-party accounts or variables here, and the account will be used by all team members.
value_not_return_tip: After the parameters are configured, they will not return to the front end again and do not need to be leaked to other members.
value_placeholder:
Enter parameter values. 
Entering a null value means deleting the configuration.
